<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>首爾家族追星雙軌之旅 5天4夜</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #1a1a2e;
            --ink-light: #3d3d5c;
            --cream: #faf8f3;
            --warm-white: #ffffff;
            --accent-red: #c0392b;
            --accent-gold: #b8860b;
            --accent-navy: #1b3a6b;
            --accent-teal: #0d7377;
            --accent-pink: #c0576b;
            --accent-soft: #e8e0f0;
            --border: #e0dbd0;
            --day-bg: #f5f2eb;
            --star-color: #c0576b;
            --tour-color: #1b3a6b;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background: var(--cream);
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* ── 列印 ── */
        @media print {
            .no-print { display: none !important; }
            body { background: white; font-size: 12px; }
            .day-card { break-inside: avoid; page-break-inside: avoid; border: 1px solid #ccc !important; box-shadow: none !important; }
            .print-break { page-break-before: always; break-before: always; }
            .print-avoid { break-inside: avoid; page-break-inside: avoid; }
            header { -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; print-color-adjust: exact; height: 180px !important; }
            .header-bg { background: #1b3a6b !important; }
        }

        /* ── 列印按鈕 ── */
        .print-btn {
            position: fixed; bottom: 2rem; right: 2rem; z-index: 100;
            background: var(--accent-navy); color: white;
            border: none; border-radius: 50%; width: 52px; height: 52px;
            font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(27,58,107,0.35);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .print-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.08); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(27,58,107,0.45); }

        /* ── Header ── */
        header {
            position: relative;
            background-color: var(--accent-navy);
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(27,58,107,0.92) 0%, rgba(13,115,119,0.85) 100%),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1538485399081-7191377e8241?q=80&w=2054&auto=format&fit=crop');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            min-height: 280px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg, transparent, transparent 60px,
                rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 60px, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 61px
            );
        }
        .header-inner {
            position: relative; z-index: 1;
            text-align: center; color: white; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
        }
        .header-eyebrow {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .header-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
            font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .header-sub {
            font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
            font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        .header-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 0.35rem 1.25rem;
            font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        /* ── Main ── */
        main { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }

        /* ── Section title ── */
        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-navy);
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
        }

        /* ── Info grid ── */
        .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }

        .info-card {
            background: var(--warm-white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--accent-navy);
        }
        .info-card.pink { border-top-color: var(--accent-pink); }
        .info-card.teal { border-top-color: var(--accent-teal); }

        .info-card-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        .info-card-title.blue { color: var(--accent-navy); }
        .info-card-title.pink { color: var(--accent-pink); }
        .info-card-title.teal { color: var(--accent-teal); }

        .flight-block {
            background: #f0f4fb; border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .flight-block strong { display: block; color: var(--accent-navy); margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .highlight-red { color: var(--accent-red); font-weight: 700; }

        .info-list { list-style: none; font-size: 13px; }
        .info-list li { padding: 0.3rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
        .info-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .info-list li::before { content: '›'; color: var(--accent-navy); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

        .field-row { background: #f5f5f0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 13px; }
        .field-row span { color: #aaa; font-size: 12px; }

        /* ── Day cards ── */
        .days-wrapper { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }

        .day-card {
            background: var(--warm-white);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .day-header {
            padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
        }
        .day-header.dark { background: var(--ink); color: white; }
        .day-header.navy { background: var(--accent-navy); color: white; }

        .day-header-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700;
        }
        .dual-badge {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            border-radius: 2rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.85rem;
            font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .day-body { padding: 1.5rem; }

        /* Single track timeline */
        .timeline { border-left: 2px solid var(--border); padding-left: 1.25rem; }
        .tl-item { position: relative; padding-bottom: 1.25rem; }
        .tl-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
        .tl-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; left: -1.45rem; top: 5px;
            width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent-navy); border: 2px solid var(--warm-white);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-navy);
        }
        .tl-time { font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-navy); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .tl-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 3px; }
        .tl-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-light); }

        .tl-item.red .tl-time { color: var(--accent-red); }
        .tl-item.red::before { background: var(--accent-red); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-red); }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #fff8e8;
            border: 1px solid #f0d080;
            border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 13px;
        }
        .highlight-box strong { color: #7a5800; display: block; margin-bottom: 3px; }

        /* Dual track grid */
        .dual-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .dual-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .track {
            border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
        }
        .track.star { background: #fdf0f3; border: 1px solid #f0c8d0; }
        .track.tour { background: #eef3fb; border: 1px solid #c0d0e8; }

        .track-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
        }
        .track-title.star { color: var(--accent-pink); }
        .track-title.tour { color: var(--accent-navy); }

        .track-list { list-style: none; font-size: 13px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
        .track-list li strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 1px; }
        .track-list li { padding-bottom: 0.7rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border); }
        .track-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }

        .meetup-row {
            background: var(--day-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.9rem;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .meetup-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
        .meetup-text strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 3px; }

        /* notice */
        .notice {
            background: #f0f4fb; border: 1px solid #c0d0e8;
            border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem 1rem; margin-top: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent-navy);
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        footer {
            background: var(--ink); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
            text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem;
            font-size: 12px; margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        footer span { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

        a { color: var(--accent-teal); text-decoration: underline; }
        a:hover { color: var(--accent-navy); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<button onclick="window.print()" class="print-btn no-print" title="列印 / 存為 PDF">
    <i class="fas fa-print"></i>
</button>

<header>
    <div class="header-inner">
        <p class="header-eyebrow">Family K-Trip · 6大6小</p>
        <h1 class="header-title">首爾家族追星雙軌之旅</h1>
        <p class="header-sub">弘大為營 · 追星與休閒的完美平衡</p>
        <span class="header-badge">2025.07.17 (四) ─ 2025.07.21 (一)　5天4夜</span>
    </div>
</header>

<main>

    <!-- ══ 重要資訊 ══ -->
    <section class="print-avoid">
        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-circle-info" style="color:var(--accent-navy);font-size:1rem;"></i> 行程重要資訊</h2>
        <div class="info-grid">

            <!-- 航班 -->
            <div class="info-card">
                <p class="info-card-title blue"><i class="fas fa-plane-departure"></i> 航班資訊</p>
                <div class="flight-block">
                    <strong>去程 (7/17) · 台灣虎航 IT662</strong>
                    16:00 高雄 (KHH) → <span class="highlight-red">19:45 金浦 (GMP)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flight-block">
                    <strong>回程 (7/21) · 德威航空 TW671</strong>
                    <span class="highlight-red">13:05 仁川 (ICN) T1</span> → 15:10 高雄 (KHH)
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 住宿 -->
            <div class="info-card pink">
                <p class="info-card-title pink"><i class="fas fa-house-user"></i> Airbnb 住宿（弘大）</p>
                <p style="font-size:13px;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">
                    <strong>房源連結：</strong>
                    <a href="https://www.airbnb.com.tw/rooms/36014472" target="_blank">點擊查看（出發前請確認仍上架）</a>
                </p>
                <div class="field-row">韓文地址：<span>（請向房東索取後填入）</span></div>
                <div class="field-row" style="margin-top:0.4rem;">大門密碼：<span>（請向房東索取後填入）</span></div>
                <div class="notice" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock" style="margin-right:4px;"></i>
                    <strong>退房提醒：</strong>一般 Airbnb 退房時間為 11:00，Day 5 出發前請確認房東要求。
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 攻略 -->
            <div class="info-card teal">
                <p class="info-card-title teal"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> 實用攻略 &amp; 外送</p>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li><span><strong>交通票券：</strong>機場超商購買 WOWPASS 或 T-Money 儲值卡。</span></li>
                    <li><span><strong>叫車神器：</strong>大人手機必載 <strong>Kakao T</strong>（綁台灣信用卡），12人短程叫3台最省事。</span></li>
                    <li><span><strong>外送大絕：</strong>下載 <strong>Creatrip App</strong>，輸入韓文地址＋大門密碼，用 LINE Pay 叫炸雞直送 Airbnb！</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ══ 逐日行程 ══ -->
    <section class="print-break">
        <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-calendar-days" style="color:var(--accent-navy);font-size:1rem;"></i> 逐日雙軌行程表</h2>

        <div class="days-wrapper">

            <!-- Day 1 -->
            <div class="day-card print-avoid">
                <div class="day-header dark">
                    <span class="day-header-title">Day 1 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7/17 (四)　抵達首爾與炸雞派對</span>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="timeline">
                        <div class="tl-item">
                            <p class="tl-time">19:45</p>
                            <p class="tl-title">🛬 抵達金浦機場（GMP）&amp; 入境</p>
                            <p class="tl-desc">搭乘機場快線 AREX 前往弘大，車程約 15 分鐘。建議在機場超商購買 T-Money / WOWPASS 儲值卡。</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tl-item">
                            <p class="tl-time">21:30</p>
                            <p class="tl-title">🏡 弘大 Airbnb Check-in</p>
                            <p class="tl-desc">安頓行李，整理住宿環境。</p>
                            <div class="highlight-box">
                                <strong>🍗 宵夜：Creatrip 叫外送炸雞派對</strong>
                                全家安頓好後，使用 Creatrip App 點半半炸雞，在客廳舉辦第一晚的接風派對！
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 2 -->
            <div class="day-card print-avoid">
                <div class="day-header navy">
                    <span class="day-header-title">Day 2 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7/18 (五)　江南潮流與追星初體驗</span>
                    <span class="dual-badge">雙軌日</span>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="dual-grid">
                        <div class="track star">
                            <p class="track-title star"><i class="fas fa-star" style="font-size:13px;"></i> 追星小隊（孩童＋陪同大人）</p>
                            <ul class="track-list">
                                <li><strong>上午</strong> JYP 娛樂朝聖（江東區）<br>打卡新大樓，周邊應援咖啡廳巡禮。</li>
                                <li><strong>下午</strong> K-Pop Square（三成站）<br>觀賞巨大 3D 螢幕偶像廣告。</li>
                                <li><strong>傍晚</strong> AK Plaza（弘大）<br>提早回弘大逛 Withmuu，購買專輯周邊。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="track tour">
                            <p class="track-title tour"><i class="fas fa-mug-hot" style="font-size:13px;"></i> 觀光小隊（大人）</p>
                            <ul class="track-list">
                                <li><strong>上午</strong> 樂天世界塔 Seoul Sky<br>登高俯瞰首爾，或漫步石村湖畔。</li>
                                <li><strong>下午</strong> 星空圖書館 &amp; COEX Mall<br>拍網美照、吹冷氣悠閒購物。</li>
                                <li><strong>傍晚</strong> 延南洞漫步<br>逛文青小店與京義線林蔭道。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meetup-row">
                        <span class="meetup-icon">🤝</span>
                        <div class="meetup-text">
                            <strong>晚餐會合：弘大商圈</strong>
                            大吃韓式烤肉（給豚的男人 / 八色烤肉），飯後欣賞弘大街頭 Busking 舞蹈表演。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 3 -->
            <div class="day-card print-avoid">
                <div class="day-header navy">
                    <span class="day-header-title">Day 3 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7/19 (六)　聖水洞布魯克林與漢江之夜</span>
                    <span class="dual-badge">雙軌日</span>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="dual-grid">
                        <div class="track star">
                            <p class="track-title star"><i class="fas fa-star" style="font-size:13px;"></i> 追星小隊</p>
                            <ul class="track-list">
                                <li><strong>上午</strong> Cube 娛樂朝聖（聖水洞）<br>尋找 (G)I-DLE 經紀公司足跡。</li>
                                <li><strong>下午</strong> 聖水洞快閃店巡禮<br>逛各大娛樂公司常辦 Pop-up Store 的街區。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="track tour">
                            <p class="track-title tour"><i class="fas fa-mug-hot" style="font-size:13px;"></i> 觀光小隊</p>
                            <ul class="track-list">
                                <li><strong>上午</strong> 首爾林散步<br>享受都市叢林中的自然寧靜。</li>
                                <li><strong>下午</strong> 聖水洞特色咖啡廳<br>Dior 概念店打卡，Cafe Onion 老屋喝咖啡。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meetup-row">
                        <span class="meetup-icon">🤝</span>
                        <div class="meetup-text">
                            <strong>晚餐會合：纛島漢江公園</strong>
                            全家在漢江邊叫外送野餐（炸醬麵或炸雞），享受韓國最道地的夏日傍晚。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 4 -->
            <div class="day-card print-avoid">
                <div class="day-header navy">
                    <span class="day-header-title">Day 4 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7/20 (日)　傳統韓服與最後血拼</span>
                    <span class="dual-badge">雙軌日</span>
                </div>
                <div class="day-body">
                    <div class="dual-grid">
                        <div class="track star">
                            <p class="track-title star"><i class="fas fa-star" style="font-size:13px;"></i> 追星小隊</p>
                            <ul class="track-list">
                                <li><strong>上午</strong> 明洞 Music Korea<br>尋找絕版專輯，逛 Olive Young 旗艦店買美妝。</li>
                                <li><strong>下午</strong> 弘大／合井 Soundwave<br>最後補齊遺漏的周邊。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="track tour">
                            <p class="track-title tour"><i class="fas fa-mug-hot" style="font-size:13px;"></i> 觀光小隊</p>
                            <ul class="track-list">
                                <li><strong>上午</strong> 景福宮 &amp; 韓服體驗<br>體驗傳統文化，拍下美好的家族合照。</li>
                                <li><strong>下午</strong> 益善洞韓屋村<br>穿梭在傳統韓屋改建的文青巷弄中。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meetup-row">
                        <span class="meetup-icon">🤝</span>
                        <div class="meetup-text">
                            <strong>晚餐會合：廣藏市場 或 東大門</strong>
                            品嚐綠豆煎餅、生拌牛肉，或到東大門吃陳玉華一隻雞，飯後可逛 DDP 建築夜景。
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 5 -->
